						<h6>How do I tag an issue so it becomes a task?</h6>
						<p>
dhfjdhsfjsdhfkj						</p>
					</div>
					</li>

					<!-- FEATURE -->
					<li>
					<!-- ICON -->
					<div class="icon-container pull-left">
						<span class="icon_tool"></span>
					</div>
					<!-- DETAILS -->
					<div class="details pull-left">
						<h6>Can I modify a task price offer?</h6>
						<p>
							Yes, simply add a comment to the issue with a new price tag. The last one always counts (<a data-toggle="modal" role="button" href="#modify-task-price-example">see example</a>).
						</p>
